'''Medlifter troop transports''', also know simply as '''medlifter transports''' or '''medlifters''', were [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeders]] designed to [[Transport/Legends|transport]] wounded soldiers from the battlefield to mobile field hospitals. The [[Ubrikkian Transports/Legends|Ubrikkian Transports]] [[Model 300]] was the medlifter most commonly used by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].<ref name="TCWCG">''[[The Clone Wars Campaign Guide]]''</ref> The medlifter model used on [[Drongar/Legends|Drongar]] could hold six [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]].

